---
import ToolLayout from '../../components/tools/ToolLayout.astro';
import { findTool } from '../../data/tools';

const tool = findTool('anticoagulant-hold');
---

<ToolLayout tool={tool}>
  <aside class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 bg-amber-50 p-5 mb-6 text-sm chinese-line-height">
    <p class="font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">⚠️ 臨床決策支援工具</p>
    <p class="text-amber-900">
      此工具依 ACC/AHA 2017、2022 圍術期指引、CHEST 2022 抗血栓指引簡化整理。
      <strong>最終停藥決定與是否需要 LMWH bridging 須由原處方心血管 / 神經內科醫師、外科醫師與麻醉醫師共同評估</strong>，
      不可單憑此工具自行停藥(尤其機械瓣膜、近期 VTE、近期支架植入者)。
    </p>
  </aside>

  <form id="ac-form" class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 space-y-6 print:hidden">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 font-headline">輸入資料</h2>

    <div>
      <label for="drug" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">藥物</label>
      <select id="drug" name="drug" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 bg-white focus:border-primary focus:outline-none">
        <option value="">— 請選擇 —</option>
        <optgroup label="抗血小板藥物">
          <option value="aspirin">Aspirin(Bokey 伯基 / 阿斯匹林)</option>
          <option value="clopidogrel">Clopidogrel(Plavix 保栓通)</option>
          <option value="ticagrelor">Ticagrelor(Brilinta 百無凝)</option>
        </optgroup>
        <optgroup label="維他命 K 拮抗劑">
          <option value="warfarin">Warfarin(Coumadin 可邁丁)</option>
        </optgroup>
        <optgroup label="新型口服抗凝血劑 DOAC">
          <option value="apixaban">Apixaban(Eliquis 艾必克凝)</option>
          <option value="rivaroxaban">Rivaroxaban(Xarelto 拜瑞妥)</option>
          <option value="dabigatran">Dabigatran(Pradaxa 普栓達)</option>
          <option value="edoxaban">Edoxaban(Lixiana 里先安)</option>
        </optgroup>
      </select>
    </div>

    <div>
      <label class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">手術 / 介入的出血風險</label>
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="bleedRisk" value="low" class="mt-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900">低出血風險</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">白內障、不切片內視鏡、皮膚小手術、牙科簡單拔牙</div>
          </div>
        </label>
        <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="bleedRisk" value="moderate" class="mt-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900">中度出血風險</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">內視鏡切片 / 息肉切除、腹腔鏡膽囊、一般中等手術</div>
          </div>
        </label>
        <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer">
          <input type="radio" name="bleedRisk" value="high" class="mt-1">
          <div>
            <div class="font-medium text-slate-900">高出血風險</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">神經外科、脊椎、大血管、心臟、肝/胰大手術、攝護腺切除</div>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <label for="surgeryDate" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">預定手術日期</label>
      <input type="date" id="surgeryDate" name="surgeryDate" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 focus:border-primary focus:outline-none">
    </div>

    <div id="doacFields" class="hidden">
      <label for="crcl" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">eGFR / CrCl (mL/min) <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">DOAC 使用者必填</span></label>
      <input type="number" id="crcl" name="crcl" min="5" max="200" step="1" placeholder="例如:75" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 focus:border-primary focus:outline-none">
    </div>

    <div>
      <label for="indication" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">用藥適應症</label>
      <select id="indication" name="indication" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 bg-white focus:border-primary focus:outline-none">
        <option value="">— 請選擇 —</option>
        <option value="afib">心房顫動(AF)中風預防</option>
        <option value="vte-acute">急性 VTE(<3 個月內 DVT/PE)</option>
        <option value="vte-chronic">慢性 VTE(>3 個月)</option>
        <option value="mech-aortic">機械主動脈瓣</option>
        <option value="mech-mitral">機械二尖瓣</option>
        <option value="stent-recent">近期冠脈支架(< 6 個月)</option>
        <option value="stent-stable">穩定期冠脈支架(> 6 個月)</option>
        <option value="primary">一級預防(無心血管病史)</option>
        <option value="post-mi">陳舊性 MI / 缺血性中風後</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <div id="chadsField" class="hidden">
      <label for="chads" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 mb-2">CHA₂DS₂-VASc 分數 <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">AF 用,0–9 分</span></label>
      <input type="number" id="chads" name="chads" min="0" max="9" step="1" placeholder="例如:3" class="w-full rounded-lg border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 focus:border-primary focus:outline-none">
    </div>

    <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-primary text-on-primary font-bold py-3 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
      計算停藥建議
    </button>
  </form>

  <div id="ac-result" class="hidden mt-6"></div>

  <article class="max-w-none mt-10 print:hidden space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-950 font-headline">為什麼術前停抗凝血藥這麼複雜？</h2>
    <p class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700">
      抗凝血/抗血小板藥停得太短 → <strong>術中或術後出血</strong>,停得太長 → <strong>血栓事件(中風、瓣膜栓塞、支架阻塞)</strong>。
      正確停藥要同時考慮三件事:(1) 藥物本身的半衰期與排除機轉、(2) 手術的出血風險、(3) 病患原本的血栓風險。
      DOAC 還要看腎功能(CrCl),Warfarin 還要排 INR、考慮 bridging。
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mt-6">DOAC 停藥原則(ACC/AHA 2017)</h3>
    <ul class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
      <li><strong>Apixaban / Rivaroxaban</strong>(CrCl ≥ 30):低出血風險停 24 小時(末次劑量到手術)、高出血風險停 48 小時。</li>
      <li><strong>Dabigatran</strong>:腎排除依賴度高。CrCl ≥ 80:低 24h/高 48h;CrCl 50–79:低 24h/高 48–72h;CrCl 30–49:低 48h/高 96h。</li>
      <li><strong>Edoxaban</strong>:同 Apixaban 原則。</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mt-6">Warfarin + Bridging</h3>
    <ul class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
      <li>Warfarin 停藥 <strong>5 天</strong>,手術前 1 天驗 INR,目標 < 1.5。</li>
      <li>Bridging(過渡橋接,以 LMWH 補上)<strong>僅高血栓風險者需要</strong>:機械二尖瓣、CHA₂DS₂-VASc ≥ 7、近 3 個月內 VTE、近期支架 + AF。</li>
      <li>BRIDGE 試驗(NEJM 2015)顯示:中低風險 AF 患者 bridging 反增加大出血風險,不推薦。</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mt-6">抗血小板藥的關鍵差異</h3>
    <ul class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
      <li><strong>Aspirin</strong>:一級預防者術前停 7 天;二級預防(冠心症、缺血性中風後)<strong>多數情況需繼續服用</strong>,僅在神經外科、脊椎、視網膜手術停藥。</li>
      <li><strong>Clopidogrel / Ticagrelor</strong>:停 5–7 天。但近期支架(< 6 個月)患者擅自停藥有支架血栓致命風險,須先與心臟科醫師討論延後手術。</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-950 mt-6">主要參考文獻</h3>
    <ul class="chinese-line-height text-slate-700 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-sm">
      <li>Doherty JU, et al. ACC 2017 Expert Consensus Decision Pathway on Periprocedural Management of Anticoagulation in Patients With Nonvalvular Atrial Fibrillation. <em>J Am Coll Cardiol</em>. 2017;69:871.</li>
      <li>Douketis JD, et al. Perioperative Management of Antithrombotic Therapy: An American College of Chest Physicians Clinical Practice Guideline. <em>CHEST</em>. 2022;162(5):e207.</li>
      <li>Douketis JD, et al. Perioperative Bridging Anticoagulation in Patients with Atrial Fibrillation (BRIDGE Trial). <em>N Engl J Med</em>. 2015;373:823.</li>
      <li>Lawton JS, et al. 2021 ACC/AHA/SCAI Guideline for Coronary Artery Revascularization (DAPT Duration). <em>Circulation</em>. 2022;145(3):e18.</li>
    </ul>
  </article>

  <script is:inline>
    const form = document.getElementById('ac-form');
    const result = document.getElementById('ac-result');
    const drugSelect = document.getElementById('drug');
    const doacFields = document.getElementById('doacFields');
    const indicationSelect = document.getElementById('indication');
    const chadsField = document.getElementById('chadsField');

    const DOAC = ['apixaban', 'rivaroxaban', 'dabigatran', 'edoxaban'];

    drugSelect.addEventListener('change', () => {
      doacFields.classList.toggle('hidden', !DOAC.includes(drugSelect.value));
    });

    indicationSelect.addEventListener('change', () => {
      chadsField.classList.toggle('hidden', indicationSelect.value !== 'afib');
    });

    const drugDisplay = {
      'aspirin': 'Aspirin(Bokey)',
      'clopidogrel': 'Clopidogrel(Plavix)',
      'ticagrelor': 'Ticagrelor(Brilinta)',
      'warfarin': 'Warfarin(Coumadin)',
      'apixaban': 'Apixaban(Eliquis)',
      'rivaroxaban': 'Rivaroxaban(Xarelto)',
      'dabigatran': 'Dabigatran(Pradaxa)',
      'edoxaban': 'Edoxaban(Lixiana)',
    };

    function formatDate(d) {
      return d.toLocaleDateString('zh-TW', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric', weekday: 'short' });
    }

    function calculate(drug, bleedRisk, crcl, indication, chads) {
      const r = { holdHours: 0, holdLabel: '', bridging: false, bridgingNote: '', notes: [], resume: '' };

      // Warfarin
      if (drug === 'warfarin') {
        r.holdHours = 5 * 24;
        r.holdLabel = '5 天(手術前 5 天停藥)';
        r.resume = '通常術後 12–24 小時、確認止血充分後恢復原劑量。前 3 天 INR 仍偏低,需依血栓風險決定是否繼續 LMWH 直到 INR 達標。';
        r.notes.push('術前 1 天驗 INR,目標 < 1.5;若 INR > 1.5 可考慮口服 Vit K 1–2.5 mg。');
        // Bridging 判斷
        const highBridgeIndications = ['mech-mitral', 'vte-acute', 'stent-recent'];
        if (highBridgeIndications.includes(indication)) {
          r.bridging = true;
          r.bridgingNote = '此適應症血栓風險高(機械二尖瓣 / 近期 VTE / 近期支架),建議 LMWH bridging:停 Warfarin 後第 3 天起注射,術前 24 小時最後一劑(若為 enoxaparin 1 mg/kg q12h)。';
        } else if (indication === 'afib' && chads !== null && chads >= 7) {
          r.bridging = true;
          r.bridgingNote = `AF 且 CHA₂DS₂-VASc = ${chads}(≥ 7 為超高風險)。可考慮 bridging,但 BRIDGE 試驗顯示一般 AF 患者 bridging 反增加大出血,需個案討論。`;
        } else if (indication === 'mech-aortic') {
          r.bridging = false;
          r.bridgingNote = '機械主動脈瓣(無 AF / 無其他危險因子)為中低風險,通常不需 bridging(2022 CHEST)。';
        } else {
          r.bridging = false;
          r.bridgingNote = '此適應症血栓風險不高,BRIDGE 試驗(NEJM 2015)顯示常規 bridging 反而增加大出血。不建議常規 bridging。';
        }
        return r;
      }

      // DOACs
      if (DOAC.includes(drug)) {
        if (drug === 'apixaban' || drug === 'rivaroxaban' || drug === 'edoxaban') {
          // CrCl-independent for these (mostly)
          r.holdHours = bleedRisk === 'high' ? 48 : 24;
        } else if (drug === 'dabigatran') {
          if (crcl >= 80) r.holdHours = bleedRisk === 'high' ? 48 : 24;
          else if (crcl >= 50) r.holdHours = bleedRisk === 'high' ? 72 : 24;
          else if (crcl >= 30) r.holdHours = bleedRisk === 'high' ? 96 : 48;
          else r.holdHours = bleedRisk === 'high' ? 120 : 72;
        }
        const days = r.holdHours / 24;
        r.holdLabel = `${r.holdHours} 小時(約 ${days} 天)`;
        r.resume = bleedRisk === 'high'
          ? '術後 48–72 小時、止血穩定且無新出血證據後再恢復(高出血風險手術)。'
          : '術後 24 小時、止血穩定後恢復原劑量(低/中出血風險)。';
        r.notes.push('DOAC 不需 bridging:半衰期短,停藥後血栓風險窗口很短。');
        if (drug === 'dabigatran') r.notes.push(`Dabigatran 80% 經腎臟排除,本工具依您的 CrCl ${crcl} mL/min 推算。`);
        return r;
      }

      // Antiplatelets
      if (drug === 'aspirin') {
        if (indication === 'primary' && bleedRisk !== 'low') {
          r.holdHours = 7 * 24;
          r.holdLabel = '7 天(一級預防,可停藥)';
        } else if (bleedRisk === 'high' && (indication === 'post-mi' || indication === 'stent-stable')) {
          r.holdHours = 7 * 24;
          r.holdLabel = '7 天(高出血風險手術才停藥)';
          r.notes.push('一般情況二級預防者應繼續服用 Aspirin,僅在神經外科 / 脊椎 / 視網膜手術停藥。');
        } else if (indication === 'stent-recent') {
          r.holdHours = -1;
          r.holdLabel = '⛔ 不建議停藥';
          r.notes.push('近期支架(< 6 個月)停 Aspirin 有支架血栓致命風險。請先與心臟科醫師討論延後手術。');
        } else {
          r.holdHours = 0;
          r.holdLabel = '建議繼續服用';
          r.notes.push('二級預防 + 中低出血風險手術:多數研究支持繼續服用 Aspirin(包括 POISE-2)。');
        }
        r.resume = '術後 24 小時、止血穩定後恢復(若有停藥)。';
        return r;
      }

      if (drug === 'clopidogrel' || drug === 'ticagrelor') {
        if (indication === 'stent-recent') {
          r.holdHours = -1;
          r.holdLabel = '⛔ 不建議停藥(支架血栓高風險)';
          r.notes.push(`近期支架(< 6 個月)停 P2Y12 抑制劑有支架血栓致命風險。請先與心臟科醫師討論延後選擇性手術至 DAPT 期滿(BMS 1 個月、DES 至少 6 個月)。`);
          r.resume = '建議延後手術;若為急診,需 cardiology + surgery 多科共同決策。';
          return r;
        }
        r.holdHours = drug === 'ticagrelor' ? 3 * 24 : 5 * 24;
        r.holdLabel = `${r.holdHours / 24} 天`;
        r.notes.push(drug === 'ticagrelor' ? 'Ticagrelor 因可逆性 binding,停藥時間較 Clopidogrel 短。' : 'Clopidogrel 為不可逆 P2Y12 抑制劑,需 5 天讓血小板再生。');
        r.resume = '術後 24 小時恢復(可考慮 loading dose 加速效果)。';
        return r;
      }

      return r;
    }

    function diffDays(a, b) { return Math.round((a - b) / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)); }

    form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const drug = form.drug.value;
      const bleedRisk = form.bleedRisk.value;
      const crcl = form.crcl.value ? Number(form.crcl.value) : null;
      const indication = form.indication.value;
      const surgeryDate = form.surgeryDate.value ? new Date(form.surgeryDate.value) : null;
      const chads = form.chads && form.chads.value ? Number(form.chads.value) : null;

      if (!drug || !bleedRisk || !surgeryDate || !indication) {
        result.innerHTML = '<div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-red-500 bg-red-50 p-4 text-red-900">請完整填寫:藥物、出血風險、手術日、適應症。</div>';
        result.classList.remove('hidden');
        return;
      }

      if (DOAC.includes(drug) && !crcl) {
        result.innerHTML = '<div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-red-500 bg-red-50 p-4 text-red-900">使用 DOAC 必須輸入 eGFR / CrCl(影響停藥時程,Dabigatran 尤其關鍵)。</div>';
        result.classList.remove('hidden');
        return;
      }

      const calc = calculate(drug, bleedRisk, crcl, indication, chads);

      let stopDate = null, stopDateLabel = '';
      if (calc.holdHours > 0) {
        stopDate = new Date(surgeryDate);
        stopDate.setHours(stopDate.getHours() - calc.holdHours);
        stopDateLabel = formatDate(stopDate);
      }

      // 風險等級顏色
      let gradeClass = 'bg-green-50 border-green-500 text-green-900';
      let gradeLabel = '🟢 風險可管理';
      if (calc.holdHours < 0) {
        gradeClass = 'bg-red-50 border-red-500 text-red-900';
        gradeLabel = '🔴 不建議自行停藥,先延後手術';
      } else if (calc.bridging || (drug === 'warfarin' && indication === 'mech-mitral')) {
        gradeClass = 'bg-orange-50 border-orange-500 text-orange-900';
        gradeLabel = '🟠 需要 LMWH bridging';
      } else if (drug === 'warfarin') {
        gradeClass = 'bg-amber-50 border-amber-500 text-amber-900';
        gradeLabel = '🟡 中等複雜度(Warfarin + INR 監測)';
      }

      const notesHtml = calc.notes.map(n => `<li>${n}</li>`).join('');

      result.innerHTML = `
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border-l-4 ${gradeClass} p-5">
            <p class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">${gradeLabel}</p>
            <p class="text-sm">${drugDisplay[drug]} · ${bleedRisk === 'low' ? '低' : bleedRisk === 'moderate' ? '中' : '高'}出血風險手術 · ${indication}</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-950 mb-3 font-headline">📅 停藥時程</h3>
            <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
                <dt class="text-slate-500">手術日</dt>
                <dd class="sm:col-span-2 text-slate-900 font-medium">${formatDate(surgeryDate)}</dd>
              </div>
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
                <dt class="text-slate-500">停藥時長</dt>
                <dd class="sm:col-span-2 text-blue-950 font-bold">${calc.holdLabel}</dd>
              </div>
              ${stopDate ? `
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
                <dt class="text-slate-500">最後一劑時間</dt>
                <dd class="sm:col-span-2 text-blue-950 font-bold">${stopDateLabel} 之前</dd>
              </div>` : ''}
              <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 pt-2 border-t border-slate-100">
                <dt class="text-slate-500">術後恢復</dt>
                <dd class="sm:col-span-2 text-slate-700">${calc.resume}</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>

          ${calc.bridgingNote ? `
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-orange-900 mb-2 font-headline">🌉 Bridging 評估</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-orange-900 chinese-line-height">${calc.bridgingNote}</p>
          </div>` : ''}

          ${notesHtml ? `
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-200 p-5">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-950 mb-3 font-headline">📋 補充注意</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700 chinese-line-height">${notesHtml}</ul>
          </div>` : ''}

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-surface-container p-5 text-sm text-slate-700 chinese-line-height">
            <p class="font-semibold text-blue-950 mb-2">⚖️ 重要提醒</p>
